{"title":"献厚礼","authors":["栗金马"],"dates":[{"year":1982,"month":9,"day":11}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"献厚礼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"栗金马"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十二大啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十二大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"召开的喜讯飞天涯！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全国都在献厚礼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我该拿些啥？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“你说拿些啥？”——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老伴一旁接话茬："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“装点麦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带瓶蜜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捎上一枝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"芝麻花！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“别打岔！”——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老汉气得肺快炸："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“说正经的没有你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闲话淡话不少拉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁希罕这些小东西，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拿出去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不怕人笑话！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“哈、哈、哈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人都说你‘老精通’，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我看你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不如三岁小娃娃！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这几样礼物不能少，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"收拾，收拾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快走吧……”"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}